{"tid":1341263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【00:16】政府強烈譴責暴力行為","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:59:47.000Z","uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":181,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"925296ab8b6b0e933621bd1765c21fa23c16e84a","tid":1341263,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"政府強烈譴責暴力行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就昨日（七月二十一日）晚上在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為，特區政府作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n  繼之前衝擊中聯辦大樓後，再有激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一帶向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，包括投擲汽油彈、縱火、擲磚，亦堵塞主要幹道，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">  與此同時，在元朗有人聚眾在港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n  香港作為法治社會完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，特區政府予以強烈譴責，並會嚴正追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月22日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時16分"},{"pid":"d3c87802efa4e7f1102e3919f1c2ff2acce58fd8","tid":1341263,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"UP"},{"pid":"464e897ad90e0aed96845e69d895c6d46ae399e4","tid":1341263,"uid":38109,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"但差人唔做野WO"},{"pid":"9efb9c0ef8cf487559b3d3ec1b169f6361c7e8a8","tid":1341263,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"76c8850c3e8e3c78fd8bddc26dc228a204a14acd","tid":1341263,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"收檔啦"},{"pid":"8e37823095887707b9a2e4d4a544b914238f1e79","tid":1341263,"uid":146791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"即刻同我入黎like爆呢個fb page!!!上twitter推推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1340827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1340827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4173ff3d3ecce8c52c1d2c0680e145e6ae4b258a","tid":1341263,"uid":268053,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"網誌治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"